#
#   -D__GEOS__ added to identify PC/GEOS usage.
#
#	-Ot: do inline structure copies rather than calling F_SCOPY@
#	-c: suppress link
#	-v: place debugging records in the output
#	-y: place line number records in the output
#	-ml: LARGE memory model
